page.title: 20Contributors
page.content: This area was surveyed by the second year BEd students at the Polytechnic of North London, as part of their Environmental Studies course. The members of the group were: L Helman, G Patterson, A McDonagh, M D'Cruz, A Agha, J Bhandol, E Charalambous, M Jackson, Y Hidueghy, S Jayasunya, M Gadher, M Daya, G McCann, B Chilley, T Law, J Kerr, G Naylor, Z Gani, B Costas, B Clark, Y Morris, G Odogwu, J Howard, B McClemont, C Truman, A Morrison, B Smith, S Stephens, F Williams, S Wilson, G Olawore, A Robinson, A Saithna, J Tomlinson, N Groves, I Waith, I Comer, D Singh, N Din, I Jamieson and J Jones. Also A H Marks, A Holmes, D Hill, A Ross.
